### Pruebas de Performance y Alertas
@host = http://localhost:5063

### 1. Generar operación con warning (3 segundos)
GET {{host}}/api/testperformance/slow-warning
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Generar operación crítica (6 segundos)
GET {{host}}/api/testperformance/slow-critical
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Simular falla
GET {{host}}/api/testperformance/simulate-failure
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Generar 5 operaciones rápidas
GET {{host}}/api/testperformance/fast-operations/5
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Stress test completo
POST {{host}}/api/testperformance/stress-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fastOperations": 3,
    "warningOperations": 2,
    "criticalOperations": 1
}

### 6. Ver métricas del dashboard
GET {{host}}/api/metricsdashboard/health
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Ver alertas activas
GET {{host}}/api/metricsdashboard/alerts
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Ver métricas del sistema
GET {{host}}/api/metricsdashboard/system
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Dashboard web
# Abrir en navegador: {{host}}/dashboard.html
